&ldquo;A fire-breathing dragon lives in my garage&rdquo;
  Suppose (I&rsquo;m following a group therapy approach by the psychologist Richard Franklin) I seriously make such an assertion to you. Surely you&rsquo;d want to check it out, see for yourself. There have been innumerable stories of dragons over the centuries, but no real evidence. What an opportunity!
  &ldquo;Show me,&rdquo; you say. I lead you to my garage. You look inside and see a ladder, empty paint cans, an old tricycle&ndash;but no dragon.
